This is a placeholder for the audio file. To add an actual birthday song:
1. Download or create a birthday song (mp3 format)
2. Replace this file with the actual audio file using:
   - GitHub web interface (Upload files)
   - Or using git: git add birthday-song.mp3 && git commit -m "Add birthday song"
3. You can use royalty-free songs from:
   - Pixabay Music: https://pixabay.com/music/
   - Bensound: https://www.bensound.com/
   - YouTube Audio Library
   
Recommended: "Happy Birthday" instrumental or "Birthday" by Katy Perry (if rights allow)